### ============================================================================
### HEALTH PROFILES — /api/v1/health-profiles
### ============================================================================

### Get my health profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles/my
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List all health profiles (unpaginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles/all
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List health profiles (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get health profile by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles/{{healthProfileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create health profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conditions": "None",
  "medications": "None",
  "allergies": "Penicillin",
  "bloodType": "O+",
  "emergencyContactName": "Mary Thomas",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "+2348023456789",
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Update health profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles/{{healthProfileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conditions": "Asthma (mild)",
  "medications": "Ventolin inhaler",
  "allergies": "Penicillin, Sulfa",
  "bloodType": "O+",
  "emergencyContactName": "Mary Thomas",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "+2348023456789",
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Delete health profile
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health-profiles/{{healthProfileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
